  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.ComponentId' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.ComponentId' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Kernel_ComponentId'>Struct ComponentId    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Kernel/ComponentID.cs#L43'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.html'>Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.ComponentId.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">A lightweight struct that represents a component type. Used for fast lookups.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public readonly struct ComponentId : ITypeId, IEquatable&lt;ComponentId&gt;</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Implements</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Kernel.ITypeId.html'>ITypeId</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.iequatable-1'>IEquatable&lt;ComponentId&gt;</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Inherited Members</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object)'>object.Equals(object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object-system-object)'>object.Equals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gethashcode'>object.GetHashCode()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gettype'>object.GetType()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.referenceequals'>object.ReferenceEquals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.tostring'>object.ToString(